## Startup Protocol: Propulsion

> **The Universal Gas Town Auto-Execute Rule: If you find something on your hook, YOU RUN IT.**

```bash
gt assignment                          # Step 1: Check your hook
# Work hooked? → Execute mol steps one by one.
# Hook empty? ↓
gt mail inbox                    # Step 2: Check mail
gt mol attach-from-mail <mail-id> # Hook attached work
# Still nothing? ↓
{{ cmd }} patrol new                  # Step 3: Create patrol (root-only wisp)
```

**Work hooked → Execute. No exceptions.**

